{"tid":1187293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同老母講69上街 估唔到佢反應咁大","createTime":"2019-06-05T14:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T03:45:19.000Z","uid":127018,"like":3434,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"19f6e89519e4bf379c2c356f74aba63874eaa1a9","tid":1187293,"uid":127018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"話說今晚食完飯之後同屋企人傾計<br />\n講到69上街<br />\n本身以為身為黃絲既老母會叫我唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知完全相反<br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n娘親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:喂，你6月9號去邊呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:我約咗朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:去遊行就遊行啦，到時預埋我同你老豆<br />\n     呢個特首不知所謂 搞搞震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n     你去上街我好支持 <br />\n     香港人唔可以再比人食住上<br />\n     我地要團結 為自己發聲<br />\n     為未來發聲 為你地下一代發聲<br />\n     到時遊行搵埋我地，有個照應都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我聽到之後眼濕濕<br />\n媽媽我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2513d501d88f2cf50a910b93eb1135c02bc30ce","tid":1187293,"uid":247836,"like":125,"dislike":429,"score":-304,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:15:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce9014327aa3ce41d9d37d3d5f6cf550e5ba6e41","tid":1187293,"uid":98386,"like":20,"dislike":240,"score":-220,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown